dct_title_s: New York city transportation route boundaries, 2004
dct_description_sm: The "Transportation_line" dataset is a line representation of New York City transportation route boundaries. The data is comprised of line geometries with attribute information. Feature classifications include: Alley, Unpaved, Airport Runway, Driveways over 200', Concrete Boardwalk, Curbs, Wooden Boardwalk, Road Edge, Obscured Road Edge.
dct_creator_sm: New York City Department of Information Technology and Telecommunications
